{"tid":1539001,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[咪撚hea] 撤回後更應該升級行動","createTime":"2019-09-04T08:33:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T12:39:57.000Z","uid":163842,"like":58,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"59fa9fbe65dc58ba4d19b176c055360290229487","tid":1539001,"uid":163842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:33:27.000Z","msg":"原因如下:<br />\n1. 香港人善忘, Hea下hea下就完, 但中共唔會放過你<br />\n2. 大搜捕唔會完, 一放鬆只會有更多手足被捕<br />\n3. 之前捉左同受傷既手足呢?<br />\n4. 之前話壽終正寢姐係老點你, 你仲信佢?<br />\n5. 美國已經兵臨城下, 呢個時候香港人唔爭氣無人幫到你<br />\n6. 由歷史層面同監控系統發展黎睇, 今次係最後一次香港人可做到既大型反對政治既活動<br />\n7. 林鄭慣常技倆, 表面和談, 暗地清算<br />\n8. 要用行動回應, 重申五大訴求, 缺一不可<br />\n9. 選舉就到, 唔好比建制有喘息機會<br />\n<br />\n太多原因，但唔升級結果只有一個: 民憤消散，一切由內部結束<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">預計10月1前會有極大量左膠出現, 千萬唔好重搖</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1d4e6272b4508a95fa30f1e8727eb7dacaf020ad","tid":1539001,"uid":163842,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:35:21.000Z","msg":"係辛苦但請堅持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a85e8db7b5acb589cc9e5d41da270a9d86333c5b","tid":1539001,"uid":163842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:36:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">缺一不可</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1d68974fdb9828f68f426e9aa215940e31b3c471","tid":1539001,"uid":4075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:36:27.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求   缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">FIVE DEMANDS - NOT ONE LESS</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>9月7 機場<br />\n9月8 美領</strong></span></span></